comments: Williams (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Barnes (SAC) and firms up to absorb the contact.
Hield (SAC) briefly places an arm around the back of Harrell (LAC) as he runs through the lane but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Hield (SAC) wraps Harrell (LAC) in the post during the entry pass.
Harrell (LAC) bobbles the inbound pass and legally starts his dribble when he gains possession.
Hield (LAC) has a resting hand on the hip of Williams (LAC) but immediately removes it as he starts to move away.
Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Barnes (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Barnes (SAC) and Gallinari (LAC) engage and separate as they go through the screen.
Barnes (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Gallinari (LAC) and makes clean contact with the ball.
Bogdanovic (SAC) briefly grasps the arm of Beverley (LAC) but the contact does not affect his ability to go for the rebound.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) at the end of the drive.
Harrell (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hield (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) briefly places an arm on the hip of Cauley-Stein (SAC) but the contact does not affect his SQBR.

RLS shows Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Fox (SAC) and he makes incidental foot to foot contact with his teammate Harrell (LAC) that causes him to fall to the floor.
Harrell (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hield (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harrell (LAC) makes clean ball contact and does not impede Hield (SAC) during the rebound.
Bogdanovic (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Williams (LAC) and the contact to his side is marginal.
Barnes (SAC) cleanly gathers the loose ball.
RLB shows Hield (SAC) cleanly steals the ball from Harrell (LAC).
Gallinari (LAC) is in a legal guarding position when Barnes (SAC) delivers contact to his chest that dislodges him on the driving shot attempt.
Green (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hield (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beverley (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Williams (LAC).
[Observable in enhanced video] Bogdanovic (SAC) slides his pivot foot.
Thornwell (LAC) and Bogdanovic (SAC) engage and separate during the inbound.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Harrell (LAC).
